---
import MarketingLayout from '../../layouts/MarketingLayout.astro';
---

<MarketingLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Kindling"
  description="Terms of Service for Kindling, free and open source fiction writing software. MIT licensed."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="terms-updated">Last updated: February 17, 2026</p>
  </section>

  <article class="content-section terms-content">
    <h2>1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
    <p>By downloading and using Kindling, you agree to these terms. Kindling is provided under the <a href="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MIT License</a>.</p>

    <h2>2. Description of Software</h2>
    <p>Kindling is a free, open-source desktop application for fiction writers. It runs locally on your computer (macOS, Windows, Linux). It imports outline files (Plottr .pltr, yWriter .yw7, Markdown .md) and provides a scaffolded writing environment. It exports to DOCX and Markdown formats. Kindling does not require an account, internet connection, or subscription.</p>

