    <h2>4. Data & Privacy</h2>
    <p>Kindling does not collect, transmit, or store any personal data. All project files are stored locally on your computer as SQLite databases. Kindling does not communicate with any external servers. Kindling does not include analytics, telemetry, or tracking of any kind. For website data practices, see our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>5. No Warranty</h2>
