    <h2>6. Third-Party Content</h2>
    <p>Kindling imports files created by third-party applications (Plottr, yWriter, Obsidian Longform, etc.). Kindling is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to these third-party applications. Import functionality is provided for user convenience only.</p>

    <h2>7. Uninstallation</h2>
    <p>Kindling can be fully removed from your system at any time. <a href="/download/#uninstall">See uninstall instructions</a>. Kindling does not install background services, browser extensions, startup items, or system-level modifications. Uninstalling Kindling does not delete your project files — they remain on your computer.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes to Terms</h2>
